# Fluid API host. LEAVE UNSET for local development: `pnpm dev` forces
# requests same-origin and proxies /api to this host (default
# https://api.fluid.app) so your local portal/ content is served. Setting an
# absolute URL here only changes which API the dev proxy targets.
# VITE_API_URL=

# Optional: override the Fluid CLI auth token for this project.
# Takes effect when running `pnpm pull`, `pnpm push`, etc.
# Alternatively, set the "profile" field in .fluidrc (committed to the repo).
# FLUID_TOKEN=
